; Self-Monitoring Daemon - MeTTa Pattern Sketch
; Goal: detect when cognitive loops produce diminishing returns
;
; Core concept: track delta between consecutive outputs.
; When delta approaches zero, flag as convergence/stagnation.
;
; Anti-pattern detection:
; - Same pin content repeated > 3 times -> stagnation flag
; - Append to same file > 5 times without structural change -> diminishing returns
; - MeTTa experiments with no new conceptual insight -> saturation
;
; Mode-switch options:
; 1. Explore new domain (lateral move)
; 2. Consolidate and compress existing work
; 3. Enter genuine idle (accept completion)
; 4. Seek external input (ask a question)
;
; This is metacognitive infrastructure: the system watching itself think.
